'''Terry Ballantine Bisson''' (d. [[January 10]], [[2024]])<ref>https://locusmag.com/2024/01/terry-bisson-1942-2024/</ref> was a science fiction and fantasy author, who wrote the young-reader books ''[[Boba Fett: The Fight to Survive]]'' and ''[[Boba Fett: Crossfire]]'' in the [[Boba Fett (books)|''Boba Fett'']] book series.

